CHANGELOG.md:93:- Added a local Ada generation backend stub: `senseweave.generation.client_local.LocalAdaClient` now satisfies the shared `GenerationClient` Protocol shape while raising `NotImplementedError("LocalAdaClient: GPU not yet installed; use Replicate or Modal")` until the local GPU path is installed. Added focused tests and an explicit mypy check for Protocol satisfaction.
CHANGELOG.md:95:- Implemented `ModalClient` satisfying `GenerationClient` Protocol in `my-claw/tools/senseweave/generation/client_modal.py`, enabling CypherClaw to use Modal serverless for generation (CCG-012). The client computes A10G runtime cost from metadata and gracefully degrades when the `modal` SDK is not installed. Also added protocol parity tests and gated live Modal tests behind `--run-live-modal`.
CHANGELOG.md:130:- Implemented ST1-ST6 of the score-tree songwriting stack end to end: added `piece_commission.py`, `piece_brief.py`, `form_grammar.py`, `score_tree.py`, `recursive_composer.py`, `composition_gate.py`, `tracker_compiler.py`, and `piece_queue.py`; extended `repertoire_memory.py` to store structural score-tree summaries; and rewired `duet_composer.py` so tracker solo mode can commission a piece, build a complete score tree, gate it, compile it into tracker scenes, and precompose the next piece into a small persistent queue instead of treating the tracker as the composer.
