, register-band counts, lowest/highest registers, ordered quarantine reasons and runtime-voice map), JSON-safe summary stability, end-to-end agreement with `resolve_voice` / `live_voices` / `quarantined_voices` / `voices_for_role` / `covered_methods`, and fractal depth >= 2, while `tests/test_smoke_narrative_script.py` remains the regression anchor for the narrative HTTP `/healthz` + `/readyz` + bearer-token hardening surface.

